    {
      "id": "PopularPost362601",
      "post_content": "@Ideatog I'm afraid you are incorrect. There is (ironically enough) nothing about protection from everything that would protect [Progenitus](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Progenitus) from Meekstone. Meekstone neither deals damage, nor is a creature, so the only thing left would be targeting - which Meekstone simply does not do.  \n  \nThis is why cards like [Wrath of God](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Wrath of God) can still destroy otherwise protected creatures. And this is also why Meekstone is BOSS.  \n  \n(For reference: http://mtg.wikia.com/wiki/Protection)",
      "posted_by": "TopRomen",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost362601\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl06_post\">@Ideatog I'm afraid you are incorrect. There is (ironically enough) nothing about protection from everything that would protect <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Progenitus\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Progenitus\">Progenitus</a> from Meekstone. Meekstone neither deals damage, nor is a creature, so the only thing left would be targeting - which Meekstone simply does not do.<br/><br/>This is why cards like <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Wrath of God\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Wrath of God\">Wrath of God</a> can still destroy otherwise protected creatures. And this is also why Meekstone is BOSS.<br/><br/>(For reference: http://mtg.wikia.com/wiki/Protection)</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl06_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl06_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '362601'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy48961\">TopRomen</span>\r\n                                (2/9/2014 12:12:04 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent